(INTRODUCTION) Tj T*
(On Being the Person Who Admits What They Do) Tj T*
(What you are holding is a book about the neurobiology of performance. Specifically:) Tj T*
(what is happening in the brain of the person watching you, and what that means for) Tj T*
(how you design, deliver, and follow through on every performance you give.) Tj T*
(I am a behavioral strategist and mentalist based in Washington D.C. My work spans) Tj T*
(corporate keynotes, training programs, and live mentalism performance. For the past) Tj T*
(several years I have been building a practice around a simple idea: that the tools) Tj T*
(which make a mentalism performance work are the same tools that make a training) Tj T*
(program stick, a negotiation land, and a first impression become a relationship.) Tj T*
(They are the same tools because they operate on the same nervous system.) Tj T*
(The brain does not have a separate mode for entertainment and professional) Tj T*
(development. It pays attention for the same reasons in both contexts. It encodes) Tj T*
(memory through the same mechanisms. It responds to uncertainty, social signal,) Tj T*
(novelty, and resolution through identical neurobiological pathways. If you) Tj T*
(understand what those pathways are and how to engage them deliberately, you are in a) Tj T*
(categorically different position than someone who does not.) Tj T*
(That is what this book is for.) Tj T*
(What You Have Felt Before) Tj T*
(You are watching someone perform something impossible. You cannot explain it. You) Tj T*
(are not quite sure whether you want to explain it ? because part of you knows that) Tj T*
(if you understood how it worked, it would work differently. That particular feeling) Tj T*
(? the pleasure of an open question you do not entirely want to resolve ? is) Tj T*
(something specific and designable. It is not accidental. The performer who produces) Tj T*
(it is working on the same system you are experiencing.) Tj T*
(What This Book Is) Tj T*
(Part One covers the neurobiology of wonder ? the specific brain systems that) Tj T*
ET

