(CHAPTER 1) Tj T*
(Designing for Reality) Tj T*
(How the brain builds experience before it receives it ? and what that means for) Tj T*
(every performance you design.) Tj T*
(????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj T*
(There is a moment in any performance where the impossible becomes visible. Not the) Tj T*
(reveal ? the moment before it. The moment when the audience has been brought to the) Tj T*
