(whether or not the individual articles intended to. The association was built) Tj T*
(through proximity, not argument. Words that appear near each other become) Tj T*
(associated. The association becomes belief. The belief becomes invisible.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This matters for the mentalist because the same mechanism operates in individual) Tj T*
(speech. When a person talks, they do not select words randomly. The words they place) Tj T*
