(CHAPTER 19) Tj T*
(Influence Without Authority) Tj T*
(The performer in a corporate context has no formal authority whatsoever. This is,) Tj T*
(paradoxically, a meaningful advantage.) Tj T*
(????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj T*
