(something impossible. I will not make them leave with a belief about themselves or) Tj T*
(the world that I know is false and that they have no way to correct. There is a) Tj T*
(specific class of effect that plants a suggestion ? about the participant's) Tj T*
(psychology, their history, their identity ? that is designed to feel like a) Tj T*
(revelation. I don't use these. The performance contract is entertainment and wonder.) Tj T*
(It is not the right context for someone to walk away believing something false about) Tj T*
(who they are.) Tj T*
(In training and consulting: I do not produce conclusions. I create conditions for) Tj T*
(conclusions to emerge. The difference is one I test explicitly: would I be) Tj T*
(comfortable telling this client exactly what I did and why? If the answer is no ? if) Tj T*
(the training involved engineering a specific outcome without the participants') Tj T*
(awareness that the outcome was being engineered ? then I have crossed from) Tj T*
