(correlation with the quality of the performance. The length of the response was) Tj T*
(driven by social dynamics, not by what was felt.) Tj T*
(This matters because it reframes what a standing ovation actually is. It is not a) Tj T*
(verdict on your work. It is a cascade ? a social contagion that either reaches) Tj T*
(critical mass or does not, depending on conditions in the room. In threshold cascade) Tj T*
(models, one low-threshold individual rising is the mechanism. You cannot control who) Tj T*
(that person is ? but you can reduce the social cost of being first: a strong close,) Tj T*
(a clear signal, collective framing, and a room that already feels like a shared) Tj T*
(experience.) Tj T*
