(The Song Anchor Technique) Tj T*
(A specific instrumental piece plays as you are introduced ? before you speak, before) Tj T*
(the audience has formed any impression. You deliver your opening line over it. The) Tj T*
(same piece plays again at the close, fully, as you deliver your final sequence. The) Tj T*
