(The emotional state an audience is in when a performance begins shapes how they) Tj T*
(process everything that follows. Pre-show audio is the simplest and most) Tj T*
(controllable tool for managing that state. Music that creates a mood of curious) Tj T*
(anticipation ? slightly unusual or unexpected in the context ? activates novelty) Tj T*
(detection without triggering a full orienting response. The audience arrives) Tj T*
(emotionally prepared for something they cannot quite categorize. That is exactly the) Tj T*
(state you want to perform into.) Tj T*
(The Target State) Tj T*
(Not excitement ? curious openness. Mild positive arousal plus genuine attentional) Tj T*
(availability. The audience should feel something is coming that they cannot quite) Tj T*
(categorize.) Tj T*
