(????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj T*
(The way a performer is introduced has more influence on the room than most) Tj T*
(performers realize. Not because audiences carefully analyze every word. Because) Tj T*
(introductions change the state of the room before the performer begins. A weak) Tj T*
(introduction makes the performer climb uphill. A strong introduction creates) Tj T*
(borrowed certainty. A great introduction does something better still: it changes the) Tj T*
