(system detects even when the conscious mind cannot name it.) Tj T*
(Certainty Under Pressure) Tj T*
(The real test of certainty is not how you present when everything is going well. It) Tj T*
(is how you recover when something does not go as planned. The performer who treats) Tj T*
(each unexpected moment as a slight inconvenience demonstrates more certainty than) Tj T*
(the one who executes a perfect sequence. The room reads recovery. Make recovery look) Tj T*
(like range, not rescue.) Tj T*
(The Congruence Gap) Tj T*
(Congruence must hold across every touchpoint: communications, presentation, arrival,) Tj T*
(behavior during the show. A single gap ? one inconsistency between claimed and) Tj T*
(demonstrated level ? creates cognitive dissonance the client will feel but may not) Tj T*
(name.) Tj T*
(Composure as Signal) Tj T*
(How you handle a technical failure or an unexpected volunteer response demonstrates) Tj T*
(certainty more convincingly than any planned sequence. The room reads recovery. Make) Tj T*
(recovery look like range, not rescue.) Tj T*
(· · ·) Tj T*
() Tj T*
