(The discovery call or initial meeting with a potential client is a performance. It) Tj T*
(has a structure, behavioral dynamics, and a moment when the decision tips.) Tj T*
(????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj T*
(The discovery call or initial meeting with a potential client is a performance. It) Tj T*
(has a structure, it has behavioral dynamics, it has a moment when the decision tips) Tj T*
(? and most performers enter it having prepared their material rather than their) Tj T*
(observation. They are ready to answer questions. They are not reading the room.) Tj T*
(Establishing the Baseline) Tj T*
(The first two minutes of a client conversation, like the first two minutes with any) Tj T*
(person, are baseline-building time. How do they speak when they are relaxed? What is) Tj T*
(their default energy level? Where does their gaze go when they are thinking?) Tj T*
(Establishing this baseline before you offer anything gives you the calibration you) Tj T*
(need to detect what happens later in the conversation when you introduce price,) Tj T*
(availability, or specific requests.) Tj T*
(The Baseline Problem) Tj T*
(Most performers enter client calls ready to answer questions. They skip) Tj T*
(baseline-building entirely. Without it, you cannot detect the shift that tells you) Tj T*
(the decision has tipped. You are selling past the close.) Tj T*
(Third Person to First Person) Tj T*
('What does something like this cost?' is third-person framing ? evaluating. 'What) Tj T*
(would you need from us?' is first-person framing ? assuming. The switch from) Tj T*
(evaluating to assuming is the buying signal. Watch for it.) Tj T*
(State the Fee. Stop.) Tj T*
(The moment you introduce price into a client conversation, the behavioral dynamics) Tj T*
(shift. Watch for it. People who were leaning forward often sit back slightly. Eye) Tj T*
(contact that was easy frequently breaks. A pause appears where there was none. None) Tj T*
(of these signals mean the answer is no. They mean the brain has just been asked to) Tj T*
(do economic evaluation, which is a different cognitive activity from the social) Tj T*
(engagement that preceded it.) Tj T*
(When you state your fee, state it cleanly and stop. A single brief sentence about) Tj T*
(value is appropriate. More than that signals that you are not confident the number) Tj T*
(will hold on its own. The pause that follows is not rejection ? it is processing.) Tj T*
(Hold it. The first person to speak after a price is stated gives ground. Make sure) Tj T*
