(truncating the neurological process that converts surprise into memory.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Never compete with the audience's emotion. When the room gasps, stop. When someone) Tj T*
(covers their mouth, hold the frame. When eyes well up, do not fill the space with) Tj T*
(words. The audience's emotional response is the effect. Your job in that moment is) Tj T*
(to not get in the way of it.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
