() Tj T*
(Performance Application: Evaluation clusters mean the prefrontal cortex is engaged.) Tj T*
(In a sales context, this is a buying signal. On stage, it is an engagement signal.) Tj T*
(The audience member or volunteer who is evaluating is doing so because they are) Tj T*
(invested enough to process what is happening rather than passively consuming it. Do) Tj T*
