() Tj T*
(Cluster Three: Certainty Drop) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(High DRS territory. Something has changed. The behavioral shift is sharp enough to) Tj T*
(indicate that a new variable has entered the person's processing ? something that) Tj T*
(disrupted whatever they were previously settled on.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Jaw Clench \(Jc\) ? DRS 3.5. Very high stress indicator. An unspoken reaction is being) Tj T*
(physically suppressed. The masseter muscle tightens visibly.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Swallow Spike \(Sw\) ? DRS 3.0. Sudden stress activation. A topic, a word, or a moment) Tj T*
(just triggered the autonomic nervous system. The swallow is involuntary and visible.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Digit Flex \(Df\) ? DRS 2.5. Micro-tension in the hands. A suppressed stress response) Tj T*
(leaking through the extremities. The fingers flex or curl slightly.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Throat Clasp \(Thc\) ? DRS 3.5. One of the highest-weight signals in the BTE. The hand) Tj T*
(moves to the throat in a grasping or touching motion. Extreme stress, a difficult) Tj T*
(truth being confronted, or a significant emotional activation.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Freeze \(Fz\) ? DRS 3.0. Total behavioral inhibition. The person stops moving) Tj T*
(entirely. The brain is processing a significant threat or surprise and has) Tj T*
(temporarily suspended all motor output.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Performance Application: DRS 3.0+ clusters indicate the) Tj T*
(hypothalamic-pituitary-adrenal axis is activated. The volunteer is experiencing) Tj T*
(genuine stress. In performance, this means you have hit something real. The question) Tj T*
(is what you do with it. Pushing through a certainty drop will break trust and may) Tj T*
(cause genuine distress. Slowing down ? lowering your voice, softening your frame,) Tj T*
(giving the person space to process ? converts the moment from a threat into a) Tj T*
(connection. "I can see something just landed. You don't have to tell me what it is.) Tj T*
(I just want you to know I noticed." That sentence, delivered with genuine warmth) Tj T*
(after a visible certainty drop, may be the most powerful moment in your show.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The Five C's of Behavioral Reading) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Before you read a single BTE signal, five principles govern everything. These are) Tj T*
(not guidelines ? they are the architecture without which individual signals are) Tj T*
(noise.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Context. The same gesture means different things in different environments. Arms) Tj T*
