(Scientific, Behavioral, and Performance Terms) Tj T*
(Superscript numbers in the text \(e.g. amygdala˛\) refer to entries in this glossary.) Tj T*
(1.  Absorption  A stable tendency to become deeply and genuinely immersed in sensory) Tj T*
(or imaginative experience. The primary trait predicting hypnotic responsiveness ?) Tj T*
