(\(1948\) and P.T. Barnum. The mechanism cold reading has exploited since the practice) Tj T*
(began: context does most of the work, content needs only to be plausible.) Tj T*
(5.  Baseline  The behavioral norm for a specific individual under neutral) Tj T*
(conditions. Meaningful behavioral reading ? micro-expressions, compliance signals,) Tj T*
